README

This program tests the function of the classes CPipe and CPipeFile. Its
configuration is in the file config.h and has to be set before build.

The program creates multiple writer and reader tasks, which all operate on the
same pipe. Each writer generates up to MAX_WRITES times a random number of
random data bytes and sends them to the pipe. Each reader tries to read up to
MAX_READS times up to MAX_READ_BYTES bytes. Sent and received data will be
displayed via the screen or serial interface to be able to compare them
manually, if necessary.
